Company Profile:SportSanity
SG is a one-stop sports portal created for sports lovers. Through a variety of platforms,
we provide an array of services that connects all in the sports fraternity - from sports enthusiasts and coaches to retailers and fans.
Quite simply, we connect sporting Singapore.
Job Description:Intern will participate in the day to day running of the business as well as the SportSanity's strategic decisions. Some example of the tasks the intern will partake in include- Event organization and planning- Liasing with coaches and retailers- Assist in planning and implementation of the company's marketing plan- Engage in meetings with SportSanity's partners - Represent SportSanity in sports events- Build relationships with new coaches & retailers- Building of new sports
